        </p>  
        <p>
            Furthermore, six sigma is now part of the culture, with 21 certified green belt and 3 certified black belts. All projects are documented and shared within Visteon plants to ensure best business practice implementations. Managing improvement projects, conduct workshops (Lean Academy, Green Belt Workshop, Energy Hunt, Waste Walk, Recognize & Define), and CI roadmap monitoring are the main activities of the OPEX team.
        </p>
